              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PLATE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The exposures were monitored using a reaction",
                "characteristic of the N-14  nucleus, protons",
                "corresponding to the first and second states from the",
                "reaction N-14(d,p)N-15* being recorded in a nuclear",
                "plate mounted at a fixed angle to the incoming beam.",
                "The number of protons recorded in the spectrograph",
                "plates could then be normalised by counting the number",
                "in a given area of monitor plate."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets consisted of a layer of adenine, C5N5H5, of",
                "thickness about 0.03 mg/cm2 evaporated on to a gold",
                "foil backing of thickness 0.2 to 0.4 mg/cm2."
              ]
            }
